Hello Tanaka-san,

I hope this message finds you in good health and high spirits! I am an environmental monitoring officer specializing in water quality. Please allow me to provide you with a comprehensive overview of our current data for your reference.

The data includes vital information about the water quality at your location. Specifically, we have observed the following variables:

